  [Text] Pyongyang, April 10 (KCNA) -- The South Korean 
rulers are driving the situation on the Korean peninsula to a 
grave phase, making much ado as if a war were imminent due to 
the North. Commenting on this, NODONG SINMUN today states that 
it is not the North but the Kim Yong-sam traitor clique of South 
Korea who are scheming a war on the Korean peninsula. 
  The news analyst says: 
