<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Deputy Foreign Minister Surin Phitsuwan has called 
for restraint and understanding in relations with Cambodia, 
saying Thailand cannot respond to the daily accusations by Phnom 
Penh of its support for the Khmer Rouge. 
  The government should be firm and act maturely as the 
Cambodian allegations could be made for domestic gain or to 
