BFN 

  [Text] Tokyo, April 11 KYODO -- Japan expressed its support 
Monday for air strikes by two NATO aircraft Sunday on Bosnian 
Serb forces advancing on the Moslem town of Gorazde in Bosnia. 
  Chief Cabinet Secretary Masayoshi Takemura told a news 
