<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   New Delhi Hosts International Chuche Seminar </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Delhi Hosts International Chuche Seminar </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Regional Chuche Board Meets </H4>

<F P=102> SK1004085494 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0844 GMT 10 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1004085494 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 10 (KCNA) -- The seventh board 
meeting of the Asian Regional Institute of the Chuche Idea 
(ARIJI) was held in New Delhi on April 8. 
  The meeting reviewed the activities of the ARIJI after its 
sixth board meeting and discussed future tasks. 
  ARIJI Secretary General Govind Narain Srivastava made a 
report titled "Let Us More Energetically Study and Disseminate 
the Chuche Idea To Achieve Asian Independence". 
  The reporter said the achievements in the institute 
activities in the period of review are that it has been proved 
through realities that the confidence in socialism of chuche has 
rooted in the minds of the Asian followers of the chuche idea as 
a strong ideological pillar unshaken in any trial and the study 
and dissemination of this idea have been conducted in various 
forms and ways in close combination with the specific conditions. 
  "Those brilliant achievements are a precious fruition of the 
wise guidance and deep solicitude of the great leader His 
Excellency President Kim Il-song and the dear leader His 
Excellency Kim Chong- il," he added, and said: 
  "We are facing an honorable task at present to consolidate 
and develop these achievements and make a positive contribution 
to bringing about a turn in the consciousness of the popular 
masses who have risen up in accomplishing the noble cause of 
building an independent, new world. Outlining the task, he said: 
  "If the study and dissemination of the chuche idea are to be 
developed in conformity with the requirement of the realities, 
greater efforts should be directed to the study and 
dissemination of the ideas and theories of the dear leader His 
Excellency Kim Chong-il. 
  "In recent years His Excellency Kim Chong-il has developed 
and enriched the chuche idea and published many monumental works 
giving profound answers to the urgent problems raised by the 
present era. 
  "We should conduct brisk activities for the publication and 
dissemination of these works, study and disseminate the chuche 
idea with them as the basic textbooks, and study, analyse and 
solve the practical problems on the basis of the profound ideas 
expounded in the works. 
  We should expand the ranks of the followers of the chuche 
idea and, on this basis, broaden our organizations and 
strengthen ideological and moral unity and cohesion of their 
members, thus making our organizations a model for the 
collectives of socio-political life which serve the people's 
cause of independence. 
  "Clearly conscious that defending Korean socialism is 
immediately to defend our own idea, we should lift up louder 
voices exposing and denouncing the imperialists' anti-socialist 
moves and closely rally all the socialist forces under the 
banner of the Pyongyang declaration. And we should wage a 
vigorous movement against a nuclear war in Korea, solidarizing 
with anti-war, peace organizations and make a positive 
contribution to an early realization of the proposal for 
founding the Democratic Confederal Republic of Koryo, mindful of 
the important position of the independent and peaceful 
reunification of Korea in achieving the independence and peace 
of our continent. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

