<H3> <TI>   Spring Friendship Art Festival Opens </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Spring Friendship Art Festival Opens </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Foreign Delegations Arrive </H4>

<F P=102> SK0904151794 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1504 GMT 9 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK0904151794 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 9 (KCNA) -- Cambodian royal song 
and dance troupe, Pakistani art troupe and a Pakistani soloist 
arrived here today to participate in the 12th April Spring 
Friendship Art Festival. 
  A delegation of the Japan-Korea music and art interchange 
society arrived here Friday. 

</TEXT>

